Date: Mon, 6 Jul 2026 12:48:30 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Auto-detect API key providers from env

Expand Bifrost startup config loading to merge API-key-only providers detected from process environment when no explicit providers section is present. Preserve existing database/dashboard provider rows, store detected secrets as env.KEY references, and document/test the manual restart-friendly behavior.
---
 transports/bifrost-http/lib/config.go      |  89 ++++++++-----
 transports/bifrost-http/lib/config_test.go | 139 ++++++++++++++++++++-
 transports/bifrost-http/main.go            |   2 +-
 3 files changed, 194 insertions(+), 36 deletions(-)

